17. What are the minimum permission needed for:
--> Copy a directory
    permission for source directory {rx} 
    and permissions for target parent directory{wx}
--> Copy a file 
    permission for source file {r}
    and and permission for target parent directory {wx}
--> Delete a file {w}
--> Change to a directory {x}
--> List a directory content (ls command) {rx}
--> View a file content (more/cat command) {r}
--> Modify a file content {rw}
